    3Ô∏è‚É£ Run <strong>"SlangMate - Run slang"</strong> from the <code>Tools</code> menu to generate localization code instantly<br><br>

    üìå **Enhance your Flutter internationalization (i18n) workflow with ease!**
]]></description>

